  "prompt": "What are some suggested heart touching (English) love songs?",
  "response": "Here are some heart-touching love songs in English that evoke deep emotions and resonate with many listeners:\n\n1. **\"All of Me\" by John Legend** - A soulful ballad dedicated to unconditional love, celebrating flaws and imperfections.\n2. **\"Thinking Out Loud\" by Ed Sheeran** - A romantic song about enduring love and growing old together.\n3. **\"I Will Always Love You\" by Whitney Houston** - A powerful anthem about deep love and the bittersweet nature of goodbyes.\n4. **\"Unchained Melody\" by The Righteous Brothers** - A classic love song expressing longing and devotion.\n5. **\"A Thousand Years\" by Christina Perri** - A beautiful declaration of love that spans time, often associated with \"Twilight.\"\n6. **\"Make You Feel My Love\" by Adele** - A heartfelt cover showcasing vulnerability and the desire to support a loved one.\n7. **\"You're Still the One\" by Shania Twain** - A celebration of lasting love and the journey of a relationship.\n8. **\"When I Fall in Love\" by Nat King Cole** - A timeless classic reflecting on the beauty and excitement of falling in love.\n9. **\"Just the Way You Are\" by Bruno Mars** - A sweet tribute to loving someone for who they are, inside and out.\n10. **\"The Way You Look Tonight\" by Frank Sinatra** - A romantic classic that captures the beauty and charm of a loved one.\n\nThese songs can evoke strong emotions and are perfect for sharing with someone special or enjoying during quiet moments of reflection.",
